            "title": "美股銀行板塊盤前延續跌勢 市場聚焦地區性銀行財報",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"965\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/hV.I7QOgUozIOr5mdLA1tw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTk2NTtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/8467aeb36c8bc96d80ab4171603592c8\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 美國的銀行類股周五盤前交易中延續跌勢，此前地區性銀行股遭遇重挫，引發亞洲和歐洲交易時段的連鎖反應。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">截至紐約時間4:40，美國銀行、花旗集團、摩根士丹利和富國銀行股價均下跌逾1.5%。此前，地區性銀行股周四大幅下挫，其中Zions Bancorp和Western Alliance Bancorp領跌，兩家機構均表示成為欺詐受害者，涉及向投資不良商業抵押貸款的基金放貸。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">周五盤前交易時段，地區性銀行股成交量有限，但Zions股價仍下跌1.8%。周四標普地區銀行精選行業指數跌6.3%，此次拋售潮令人聯想到4月時關稅引發的暴跌，以及2023年危機期間該板塊遭受的重創。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-49947858-7117-3756-af80-f100e35a73f9-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">市場焦點將迅速轉向該類銀行最新財報，多家大型地區性銀行將於紐約開盤前公佈業績。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Ginjer AM執行長Leonard Cohen表示，「投資者理所當然地感到擔憂，在類似情形下總是如此，因為他們尚未識別出風險所在」</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"965\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/09ocqCk7VOnC1E6BAoNA3Q--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTk2NTtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/181b027b211654f7e717582aaf10ea04\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題US Bank Stocks Rout Deepens as Investors Brace for Earnings</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Georgie McKay.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
